Class FXDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jpedal.examples.viewer.gui.javafx.dialog.FXDialog
  • Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class FXDialog
extends Object
    Allows for Dialog windows to be created. e.g. properties windows, input dialogs.
